    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://theme.projektemacher.org/posts/post-specific-assets/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://theme.projektemacher.org/posts/post-specific-assets/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Make sure the &lt;code&gt;assets&lt;/code&gt; directory is mounted (in &lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;config.toml&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;[module]
  [[module.mounts]]
      source = &amp;#34;assets/scss&amp;#34;
      target = &amp;#34;assets/scss&amp;#34;

  [[module.mounts]]
      source = &amp;#34;assets/js&amp;#34;
      target = &amp;#34;assets/js&amp;#34;

  [[module.mounts]]
      source = &amp;#34;assets/ts&amp;#34;
      target = &amp;#34;assets/ts&amp;#34;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add a reference to the front matter&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;scss: scss/tag-ring/tag-ring.scss
js:
  - ts/tag-ring/tag-ring.ts
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description>
      </item>
    
